race.comment: OUR COUVER (1) switched from Victoria and won here comfortably as expected over 1200m at this track last time out, dropping out early before coming home with a powerful run to score by one length. Sure to be tough to stop again. THE MEN WENT HOME (3) opened this prep beaten one length in the same contest. A distance specialist and fitter is among the top chances. FLYING START (2) will be better back up to the mile. Hasn't been having the best of it but he's good enough and has an inside gate. Keep safe. MI MIJO (4) is better than the form line suggests and has been freshened. Worth keeping onside.
